snippet.title: THE VOYAGE SINISTER - Victorian Vampire RPG
snippet.description:
The Voyage Sinister it's a Gothic story with an investigative and mystery element, set in a Victorian-inspired world. Its main character is a vampire who -during his journey to the capital- gets involved in the plot of a Dark Cult!
Itch.io: https://lilianduleroux.itch.io/the-voyage-sinister
GameJolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/TheVoyageSinister/874645

Music/BGM: Destiny by FLASH☆BEAT
